acceptBreedingRequest(uint256).details: Accepts a breeding request - Only the request receiver can accept it

cancelBreedingRequest(uint256).details: Cancels a breeding request - Only the request creator can cancel it

createBreedingRequest(address,uint256,ui.details: Creates a request from a specific Tamiko to another

isTamikoBreeding(uint256).details: Checks if a Tamiko is already breeding.

isTamikoOwner(uint256,address).details: Checks if an address owns a specific tokenID.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

redeemBreededEgg(uint256).details: Redeem 1 egg each once a request has been accepted and TIME_TO_BREED has passed

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
